Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Observe, propose a hypothesis, test and consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn the method of scientific thought.
